    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "If you’re like us, whenever you drive through rural areas you notice old cars "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "sitting in fields"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " or by "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            1
          ],
          1,
          "barns"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          ". Art Stevens must be the same way, because in 2015 the guy zeroed in on a "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            2
          ],
          1,
          "1941 Chevrolet Special Deluxe"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " parked in a field with a “for sale” sign in the window. Stevens was driving his "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            3
          ],
          1,
          "semi-truck"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " at the time, but he still pulled over to inquire about the car to which he felt a deep sentimental attachment."
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "blockquote",
      [
        [
          0,
          [
            4
          ],
          0,
          "Check out a field full of classic Porsches "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "here"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          1,
          "."
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "You see, Stevens had "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            5
          ],
          1,
          "learned to drive"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " in his dad’s 1941 Chevy, which was just like the car advertised for sale. However, the owner wanted more than Stevens was willing to pay. Over the course of a year, the truck driver would stop and talk to the vehicle owner whenever he was in the area. Finally, they agreed to a selling price and Stevens was able to relive many fond memories."
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      10,
      1
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "It didn’t take long for the man to "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            6
          ],
          1,
          "get the Chevy running"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          ". A mere 15 minutes after getting it off the trailer, he had the six-cylinder engine humming, proving the durability of the design. From there, two of the man’s sons along with a lifelong friend of his worked to restore the classic car. This is the thing so many non-gearheads don’t understand. They think people who love cars hate people, that they brood alone in their garage. Maybe they knew someone like that, but such a person is more of the exception than the rule. Working with friends and family on getting an old classic in good shape is a tremendous bonding experience. It also teaches patience, attention to detail, self-reliance, and dedication to a long-term goal."
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
